# TODO: Translation updated at 2026-03-05 21:40

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:7
translate spanish d9a_a4d4e8f0:

    # C "Stalker [persistent.player_name]? I come on behalf of the Queen of Zeta. Please open the gates."
    C "¿Acechador [persistent.player_name]? Vengo en nombre de la Reina de Zeta. Por favor, abre las puertas."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:8
translate spanish d9a_cb92de06:

    # Z "Again? I'm coming..."
    Z "¿Otra vez? Ya voy..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:12
translate spanish d9a_b11b05f1:

    # G "..."
    G "..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:15
translate spanish d9a_b13c41ec:

    # Z "How can I help?"
    Z "¿Cómo puedo ayudarte?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:18
translate spanish d9a_6cf9a4d0:

    # G "Greetings, Stalker."
    G "Saludos, Acechador."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:19
translate spanish d9a_ecd23274:

    # G "Our Queen sent me to summon you to the Palace. She has a new task for you."
    G "Nuestra Reina me envió a llamarte al Palacio. Tiene una nueva tarea para ti."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:20
translate spanish d9a_f351b9a3:

    # G "She will see you tomorrow morning."
    G "Te verá mañana por la mañana."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:26
translate spanish d9a_771d48a4:

    # Z "What is it?"
    Z "¿De qué se trata?" 

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:29
translate spanish d9a_5188619d:

    # G "Stalker, I am here because our Queen ask for your presence at the Palace, tomorrow."
    G "Acechador, estoy aquí porque nuestra Reina solicita tu presencia en el Palacio, mañana."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:30
translate spanish d9a_c5e4b489:

    # G "The reason being a new personal task."
    G "El motivo es una nueva tarea personal."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:36
translate spanish d9a_0db8674c:

    # Z "I am not interested in male servants."
    Z "No me interesan los sirvientes masculinos."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:39
translate spanish d9a_e54df44d:

    # G "Very funny, Stalker. Maybe you would like to tell those jokes to the Queen herself."
    G "Muy gracioso, Acechador. Quizá te gustaría contarle esos chistes a la propia Reina."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:42
translate spanish d9a_8b352b3a:

    # G "She demands your presence at the palace, tomorrow. She has a personal task for you."
    G "Ella exige tu presencia en el palacio, mañana. Tiene una tarea personal para ti."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:48
translate spanish d9a0_882ea9f1:

    # Zt "A personal task? What does she want now?"
    Zt "¿Una tarea personal? ¿Qué quiere ahora?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:51
translate spanish d9a0_e73711f0:

    # Z "We discussed the Zone the last time I saw her."
    Z "Hablamos de la Zona la última vez que la vi."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:52
translate spanish d9a0_cddb1cc6:

    # Z "You can let her know that my [persistent.da] has been informed about her request."
    Z "Puedes hacerle saber que mi [persistent.da] ha sido informada de su petición."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:55
translate spanish d9a0_1a17ac46:

    # G "From what I understand, this is a different matter entirely."
    G "Por lo que tengo entendido, esto es algo totalmente diferente."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:56
translate spanish d9a0_90718197:

    # G "Something has occurred recently for which she requires your expertise in a different field."
    G "Recientemente ha ocurrido algo para lo que necesita tu experiencia en otro campo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:57
translate spanish d9a0_87e16692:

    # G "Today one of our patrol leaders stands trial regarding the incident, and tomorrow she will have to deal with the fallout. That is all I know."
    G "Hoy se juzga a una de nuestras jefas de patrulla en relación con el incidente, y mañana tendrá que enfrentarse a las consecuencias. Eso es todo lo que sé."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:60
translate spanish d9a0_60c9d912:

    # Z "Why not today?"
    Z "¿Por qué hoy no?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:63
translate spanish d9a0_9364e775:

    # G "I was not informed. All I know is the message I delivered."
    G "No se me informó. Lo único que sé es el mensaje que entregué."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:64
translate spanish d9a0_f2e84dfe:

    # G "I will be going, take care, Stalker."
    G "Me iré, cuídate, Acechador."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:68
translate spanish d9a0_e2ab2ecf:

    # "You close the gate as he leaves..."
    "Cierras la puerta mientras él se va..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:69
translate spanish d9a0_8a71cb3c:

    # Zt "That is the second time she interrupts my routine to demand my presence."
    Zt "Es la segunda vez que interrumpe mi rutina para exigir mi presencia."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:71
translate spanish d9a0_5558e066:

    # Zt "I don't think she will mind much if I ignore her schedules and head there today."
    Zt "No creo que le importe mucho si ignoro sus planes y me dirijo allí hoy."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:73
translate spanish d9a0_bdc22fa8:

    # Zt "Screw her scheduling, I'm heading over there today."
    Zt "Que le den sus planes, voy a ir para allá hoy mismo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:74
translate spanish d9a0_d12b1a40:

    # Zt "If Talia is guarding the entrance again, she will let me through."
    Zt "Si Talia vuelve a vigilar la entrada, me dejará pasar."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:78
translate spanish d9a0_9c668195:

    # "You arrived at the royal plaza one hour later."
    "Llegas a la plaza real una hora más tarde."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:79
translate spanish d9a0_918d0619:

    # "As anticipated, Talia was on duty."
    "Como se esperaba, Talia está de guardia."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:81
translate spanish d9a0_662a4d16:

    # "After you tell her that you are going to the Queen's throne room, she lets you through without issue without issue."
    "Después de decirle que vas a la sala del trono de la Reina, te deja pasar sin problemas."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:82
translate spanish d9a0_8facca52:

    # "As you're about to enter, you hear voices from inside. You stop to listen..."
    "Cuando estás a punto de entrar, oyes voces del interior. Te paras a escuchar..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:85
translate spanish d9a0_17918041:

    # Q "Just so I am getting this right..."
    Q "Para que lo entienda bien..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:87
translate spanish d9a0_b6b2dd0d:

    # Q " You're telling me that a bunch of filthy raiders led by a purple haired woman took out your entire squad of trained soldiers?"
    Q " ¡¿Me estás diciendo que un puñado de saqueadores mugrientos liderados por una tía de pelo morado acabó con todo tu escuadrón de soldados entrenados?!"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:89
translate spanish d9a0_d75072bb:

    # Q "You're telling me that a raider gang led by some psychotic woman took down your entire squad of caravan guards?"
    Q "¿Me estás diciendo que una banda de asaltantes liderada por una mujer psicótica acabó con todo tu escuadrón de guardias de la caravana?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:92
translate spanish d9a0_6184d5e2:

    # Q "If I hadn't promoted you through the ranks myself, I would almost think you to be one of my personal jesters!"
    Q "Si no te hubiera ascendido yo misma, ¡casi pensaría que eres uno de mis bufones personales!"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:95
translate spanish d9a0_4f2cee89:

    # Q "But since I can see \"shame\" written all over your pathetic face, I have no other choice but to believe you."
    Q "Como puedo ver la \"vergüenza\" escrita en tu patético rostro, no tengo más remedio que creerte."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:98
translate spanish d9a0_db3fd5f1:

    # Q "Not that your shame makes up for the rest of your following misdeeds."
    Q "Aunque tu vergüenza no compensa el resto de tus fechorías."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:101
translate spanish d9a0_fbaf1619:

    # Q "Where would I be if it wasn't for the most loyal of my servants, who caught you in the act."
    Q "¿Dónde estaría yo si no fuera por el más leal de mis sirvientes, que te pilló in fraganti?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:102
translate spanish d9a0_db7adb08:

    # Q "Isn't that right, Sharifa?"
    Q "¿No es así, Sharifa?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:105
translate spanish d9a0_6758cc70:

    # Q "So, before judgement is passed upon you, let me review the sum of your misdeeds."
    Q "Así que, antes de juzgarte, déjame repasar la suma de tus fechorías."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:106
translate spanish d9a0_b11b05f1:

    # G "..."
    G "..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:109
translate spanish d9a0_d9ea5c41:

    # Q "Sharifa, my loyal guard..."
    Q "Sharifa, mi leal guardia..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:110
translate spanish d9a0_5a9d13da:

    # Sh "..."
    Sh "..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:113
translate spanish d9a0_84b959fb:

    # Q "We have been through so much together, and you have always been there whenever I needed a voice of reason..."
    Q "Hemos pasado por muchas cosas juntas, y siempre has estado ahí cuando he necesitado una voz sensata..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:114
translate spanish d9a0_fae31dd8:

    # Q "...regardless..."
    Q "... a pesar de todo..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:117
translate spanish d9a0_1ab1e3b1:

    # Q "...you and I understand very well that because I have total authority over all executive matters..."
    Q "... tú y yo entendemos muy bien que como tengo total autoridad sobre todos los asuntos ejecutivos..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:120
translate spanish d9a0_0df128f1:

    # Q "...I need reliable sources to make a fair judgement, especially on the things that concern me personally."
    Q "... necesito fuentes fiables para emitir un juicio justo, sobre todo en las cosas que me conciernen personalmente."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:123
translate spanish d9a0_3c99357d:

    # Q "That said, instead of him immediately coming to report on his failures as would be expected..."
    Q "Eso sí, en lugar de venir inmediatamente a informar de sus fracasos, como sería de esperar..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:126
translate spanish d9a0_94be7199:

    # Q "...you tell me that you saw him spy on me while I was resting in my personal chambers."
    Q "... me dices que le viste espiarme mientras descansaba en mis aposentos personales."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:129
translate spanish d9a0_6c7a551f:

    # Q "This is a serious accusation, Sharifa..."
    Q "Esta es una acusación seria, Sharifa..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:130
translate spanish d9a0_7cda4940:

    # Q "Everyone knows the sanctity and security of the Queen and her quarters is one of the absolute laws of our great city and my reign."
    Q "Todo el mundo sabe que la santidad y la seguridad de la Reina y sus aposentos es una de las leyes absolutas de nuestra gran ciudad y de mi reinado."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:133
translate spanish d9a0_a8148a25:

    # Q "You would never lie to me, would you, Sharifa?"
    Q "Nunca me mentirías, ¿verdad, Sharifa?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:134
translate spanish d9a0_1303cd99:

    # Sh "I would never..."
    Sh "Nunca..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:137
translate spanish d9a0_36606a27:

    # Sh "...Think about such a thing, my Queen."
    Sh "... se me ocurriría algo así, mi Reina."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:138
translate spanish d9a0_007b7cce:

    # Sh "I caught him standing at the doorstep of your chambers... staring at you for long enough."
    Sh "Le pillé de pie en el umbral de tus aposentos... mirándote fijamente durante mucho tiempo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:139
translate spanish d9a0_0664164e:

    # Sh "...And just as I wanted to step in, he left."
    Sh "... y justo cuando quería intervenir, se fue."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:142
translate spanish d9a0_52707177:

    # Sh "While I wanted to confront him on his treacherous act, I was also curious where he was going."
    Sh "Aunque quería enfrentarme a él por su acto traicionero, también tenía curiosidad por saber adónde iba."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:145
translate spanish d9a0_1df88e71:

    # Sh "He went straight to your servants' quarters to defile one of your slaves, my Queen."
    Sh "Fue directamente a los aposentos de tus sirvientes para mancillar a una de tus esclavas, mi Reina."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:146
translate spanish d9a0_dad60276:

    # Sh "He marched right in, without hesitation. I am sorry I could not prevent-"
    Sh "Entró directamente, sin dudarlo. Siento no haber podido impedirlo..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:149
translate spanish d9a0_1a815eaf:

    # Q "I am sure you did everything you could, Sharifa..."
    Q "Estoy segura de que has hecho todo lo posible, Sharifa..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:150
translate spanish d9a0_560f241e:

    # Q "...you are hereby promoted in command of my personal security detail."
    Q "... quedas ascendida al mando de mi equipo de seguridad personal."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:153
translate spanish d9a0_5a9d13da_1:

    # Sh "..."
    Sh "..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:156
translate spanish d9a0_07eea202:

    # Q "Now, where were we?"
    Q "Ahora, ¿dónde estábamos?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:157
translate spanish d9a0_a8efd260:

    # Q "Ah yes, you tried to have your way with one of my servants!"
    Q "Ah, sí, ¡intentaste aprovecharte de una de mis sirvientas!"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:160
translate spanish d9a0_ef591e8d:

    # Q "I do not take kindly to those who break into my property to take what's mine..."
    Q "No veo con buenos ojos a quienes irrumpen en mi propiedad para llevarse lo que es mío..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:163
translate spanish d9a0_d3f883fc:

    # Q "...though I can understand the temptation. The question remains, what would you have done if Sharifa hadn't stepped in?"
    Q "... aunque puedo entender la tentación. La pregunta sigue siendo: ¿qué habrías hecho si Sharifa no hubiera intervenido?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:164
translate spanish d9a0_b5ae8bdf:

    # Q "Would you have gone further than to make use of these lips?"
    Q "¿Habrías ido más allá de hacer uso de estos labios?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:167
translate spanish d9a0_59db53b1:

    # Q "How did you think to commit not {i}one{/i} but at least three separate serious offences in such a short time?"
    Q "¿Cómo se te ocurrió cometer no {i}uno{/i} sino al menos tres delitos graves distintos en tan poco tiempo?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:170
translate spanish d9a0_982bc204:

    # Q "I trusted you to patrol a settlement, to protect its caravans coming into this city and to scout for potential attacks from Adira."
    Q "Confié en ti para que patrullaras un asentamiento, para que protegieras las caravanas que llegaban a esta ciudad y para que exploraras los posibles ataques de Adira."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:171
translate spanish d9a0_8f1156c1:

    # Q "And what did you do instead? Spy on your own Queen?"
    Q "¿Y qué hiciste en su lugar? ¿Espiar a tu propia Reina?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:174
translate spanish d9a0_5eeb5976:

    # Q "Tell me, Mido..."
    Q "Dime, Mido..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:175
translate spanish d9a0_7538ae7e:

    # Q "...how far would you have gone?"
    Q "... ¿hasta dónde habrías llegado?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:178
translate spanish d9a0_6413a8e3:

    # Q "Hm?"
    Q "¿Um?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:179
translate spanish d9a0_da3fdbf1:

    # Mi "..."
    Mi "..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:182
translate spanish d9a0_bdc61a01:

    # Q "..."
    Q "..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:185
translate spanish d9a0_6206518d:

    # Q "Let us put aside your failures in the desert, for now..."
    Q "Dejemos de lado tus fracasos en el desierto, por ahora..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:186
translate spanish d9a0_00646947:

    # Q "You see, I need to be able to know and trust someone in a leadership position unconditionally..."
    Q "Verás, necesito poder conocer y confiar incondicionalmente en alguien en una posición de liderazgo..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:187
translate spanish d9a0_c4f42e19:

    # Q "...and while I may be your Queen, I know I would stand no chance against most of my guards..."
    Q "... y aunque sea su Reina, sé que no tendría ninguna posibilidad contra la mayoría de mis guardias..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:190
translate spanish d9a0_41b0574d:

    # Q "...much less against a tall and strong man like you."
    Q "... mucho menos contra un hombre alto y fuerte como tú."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:191
translate spanish d9a0_f7dc2c7f:

    # Q "So I have a question, and I promise to not hold your answer against you..."
    Q "Tengo una pregunta, y prometo no tener en cuenta tu respuesta..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:194
translate spanish d9a0_1dfff5cd:

    # Q "If I were alone in my chambers, defenseless, without any guards in sight..."
    Q "Si estuviera sola en mis aposentos, indefensa, sin ningún guardia a la vista..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:197
translate spanish d9a0_22f39067:

    # Q "...what would you do to me...?"
    Q "... ¿qué me harías...?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:200
translate spanish d9a0_da3fdbf1_1:

    # Mi "..."
    Mi "..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:206
translate spanish d9a0_69b6c3da:

    # Mi "My Queen, I..."
    Mi "Mi Reina, yo..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:209
translate spanish d9a0_851c2074:

    # Mi "I did not..."
    Mi "Yo no..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:212
translate spanish d9a0_e16404a9:

    # Mi "I failed your task in the east, my Queen. But I never meant to spy on you, or take advantage of your slave. It was a misunderstanding."
    Mi "He fracasado en tu tarea en el este, mi Reina. Pero nunca quise espiarte ni aprovecharme de tu esclava. Fue un malentendido."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:215
translate spanish d9a0_9367cecd:

    # Mi "I swore an oath to protect and serve you. I would never think of taking advantage of you like that."
    Mi "Hice un juramento para protegerte y servirte. Nunca se me ocurriría aprovecharme así de ti."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:216
translate spanish d9a0_bdc61a01_1:

    # Q "..."
    Q "..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:219
translate spanish d9a0_936a3538:

    # Q "Of course you wouldn't."
    Q "Por supuesto que no."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:220
translate spanish d9a0_3428f440:

    # Q "Now, kneel."
    Q "Ahora, arrodíllate."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:223
translate spanish d9a0_acc7df56:

    # Q "Sharifa..."
    Q "Sharifa..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:226
translate spanish d9a0_45bc1cfe:

    # Q "You know the rules, [Mi]. As a leader of your platoon you failed to lead and protect your soldiers and cowardly fled the battle."
    Q "Ya conoces las reglas, [Mi]. Como líder de tu pelotón fracasaste a la hora de dirigir y proteger a tus soldados, y huiste cobardemente de la batalla."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:229
translate spanish d9a0_5d0285e6:

    # Q "In addition to that, I implicitly believe the words of Sharifa over yours."
    Q "Además, confío plenamente en la palabra de Sharifa antes que en la tuya."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:232
translate spanish d9a0_a1e7317b:

    # Q "Spying on the Queen and preying on one of her slaves is an insult to the throne and blasphemy."
    Q "Espiar a la Reina y aprovecharse de una de sus esclavas es un insulto al trono y una blasfemia."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:233
translate spanish d9a0_a3256173:

    # Q "Word that this occurred will inevitably spread, and if there were to be no consequences to your deeds, it would set an inconceivable precedent."
    Q "Es inevitable que se corra la voz de que esto ha ocurrido, y si no hubiera consecuencias para tus actos, sentaría un precedente inconcebible."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:236
translate spanish d9a0_f29f7699:

    # Mi "But my Queen, I never took a look inside your chambers. I was merely passing by."
    Mi "Pero mi Reina, nunca espié el interior de tus aposentos. Sólo pasaba por allí."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:237
translate spanish d9a0_72fd3f7c:

    # Mi "The slave you mentioned got offered to me by one of your guards who said it was a royal offer."
    Mi "La esclava que mencionas me la ofreció uno de tus guardias que dijo que era una oferta real."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:240
translate spanish d9a0_666eae71:

    # Q "Nevertheless, the damage is done, and word will get out."
    Q "Sin embargo, el daño está hecho y se correrá la voz."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:241
translate spanish d9a0_86535bed:

    # Q "If your allegiance really is to the throne and to your Queen, then now is your last chance to prove it."
    Q "Si tu lealtad es realmente hacia el trono y hacia tu Reina, ahora es tu última oportunidad para demostrarlo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:244
translate spanish d9a0_9fb375e4:

    # Mi "I... will always be loyal."
    Mi "Yo... siempre seré leal."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:247
translate spanish d9a0_113cd7d9:

    # Q "Then tell me, soldier..."
    Q "Entonces dime, soldado..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:248
translate spanish d9a0_a0f09a73:

    # Q "What did you swear to do?"
    Q "¿Qué has jurado hacer?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:251
translate spanish d9a0_e9025d52:

    # Mi "I swore to serve the throne and the Holy Queen of Zeta, to protect both with my life..."
    Mi "Juré servir al trono y a la Santa Reina de Zeta, proteger a ambos con mi vida..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:254
translate spanish d9a0_c7a1393d:

    # Mi "...to help build a new world, after the previous was lost..."
    Mi "... para ayudar a construir un nuevo mundo, después de que el anterior se perdiera..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:257
translate spanish d9a0_c9d3abe4:

    # Mi "...to live and die for a new beginning..."
    Mi "... para vivir y morir por un nuevo comienzo..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:260
translate spanish d9a0_6ebe4f89:

    # Mi "...to live and die for the glory of Zeta and you,..."
    Mi "... para vivir y morir por la gloria de Zeta y de ti,..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:263
translate spanish d9a0_7f4337f1:

    # Mi "...my Queen."
    Mi "... mi Reina."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:267
translate spanish d9a0_8641851d:

    # Mi "Hmgh...!"
    Mi "¡Hmgh...!"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:274
translate spanish d9a0_972e86e4:

    # Q "I accept your oath as I did back then..."
    Q "Acepto tu juramento como lo hice entonces..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:275
translate spanish d9a0_42f20606:

    # Q "...but now, the time has come to show your quality."
    Q "... pero ahora, ha llegado el momento de mostrar tu calidad."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:279
translate spanish d9a0_7c1e8099:

    # Q "Your service will end soon."
    Q "Tu servicio terminará pronto."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:280
translate spanish d9a0_5a9d13da_2:

    # Sh "..."
    Sh "..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:283
translate spanish d9a0_54bb0e4d:

    # Qw "Tell me, [Mi]... how does it feel?"
    Qw "Dime, [Mi]... ¿qué se siente?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:286
translate spanish d9a0_9d767d08:

    # Mi "It... hngh... it hurts, my Queen..."
    Mi "Me... hngh... duele, mi Reina..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:289
translate spanish d9a0_582e9d73:

    # Qw "I'm sure it does. But I need you to stay strong, now."
    Qw "Seguro que sí. Pero necesito que te mantengas fuerte, ahora."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:292
translate spanish d9a0_147fc609:

    # Qw "I know you are, I can see the resilience in your eyes, and feel the tension in you..."
    Qw "Sé que lo eres, puedo ver la entereza en tus ojos y sentir la tensión en ti..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:295
translate spanish d9a0_d0e0ef7b:

    # Mi "Hmngh.."
    Mi "Hmngh.."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:296
translate spanish d9a0_1b974104:

    # Qw "Look me in the eyes as you die, [Mi]."
    Qw "Mírame a los ojos mientras mueres, [Mi]."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:299
translate spanish d9a0_739ee08a:

    # Mi "...!"
    Mi "¡...!"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:300
translate spanish d9a0_37de8f77:

    # Qw "That's right... stay strong..."
    Qw "Así es... mantente fuerte..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:303
translate spanish d9a0_f33968e7:

    # Mi "Hhn..."
    Mi "Hhn..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:304
translate spanish d9a0_dd1d3261:

    # Qw "Do you see them, the fields of reeds?"
    Qw "¿Ves los campos de cañas?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:305
translate spanish d9a0_2ea261af:

    # Mi "I..."
    Mi "Yo..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:308
translate spanish d9a0_4eafcdad:

    # Mi "{i}*exhales*"
    Mi "{i}*exhalando*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:309
translate spanish d9a0_da3fdbf1_2:

    # Mi "..."
    Mi "..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:310
translate spanish d9a0_3178201c:

    # Qw "Mido...?"
    Qw "¿Mido...?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:311
translate spanish d9a0_da3fdbf1_3:

    # Mi "..."
    Mi "..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:314
translate spanish d9a0_3af0a1a6:

    # Q "Sharifa, burn his corpse. He was killed in action, trying to defend the caravan."
    Q "Sharifa, quema su cadáver. Murió en acción, intentando defender la caravana."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:315
translate spanish d9a0_67003dfe:

    # Q "Send his family the compensation appropriate to his rank, and a personal acknowledgement from the throne, as customary..."
    Q "Envía a su familia la compensación adecuada a su rango, y un reconocimiento personal del trono, como es costumbre..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:316
translate spanish d9a0_12ad98ff:

    # Q "And have a word with the slave."
    Q "Y habla con la esclava."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:319
translate spanish d9a0_ba42a038:

    # Sh "Guards!"
    Sh "¡Guardias!"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:323
translate spanish d9a0_65c94103:

    # Sh "You heard the Queen, get him to the crematory."
    Sh "Ya habéis oído a la Reina, llevadlo al crematorio."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:329
translate spanish d9a0_d449fc97:

    # Sh "This never happened, and no one must know."
    Sh "Esto nunca ha ocurrido, y nadie debe saberlo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:332
translate spanish d9a0_bdc61a01_2:

    # Q "..."
    Q "..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:335
translate spanish d9a0_6d21d78a:

    # Q "{i}*sighs*"
    Q "{i}*suspiros*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:340
translate spanish d9a0_125a93d2:

    # Q "...?"
    Q "¿...?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:343
translate spanish d9a0_54240ada:

    # "You enter the throne room..."
    "Entras en la sala del trono..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:345
translate spanish d9a0_b4a1cf04:

    # Q "[persistent.player_name]?"
    Q "¿[persistent.player_name]?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:348
translate spanish d9a0_81b4fd73:

    # Q "What are you doing here?!"
    Q "¡¿Qué haces aquí?!"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:351
translate spanish d9a0_0047b0f5:

    # Q "I had the guard tell you to come tomorrow!"
    Q "He hecho que el guardia te diga que vengas mañana."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:355
translate spanish d9a0_33dac486:

    # Z "I didn't think you would mind me coming earlier."
    Z "No creí que te importara que viniera antes."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:357
translate spanish d9a0_5a83a184:

    # Z "And I decided to come here directly. Why did you call me?"
    Z "Y he decidido venir aquí directamente. ¿Por qué me has llamado?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:360
translate spanish d9a0_63e6174e:

    # Sh "Stalker!! You have no right to be here, kneel immediately!!"
    Sh "¡¡Acechador!! ¡¡No tienes derecho a estar aquí, arrodíllate inmediatamente!!"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:363
translate spanish d9a0_0d6b312a:

    # Q "Sharifa, enough, I got this."
    Q "Sharifa, basta, yo me encargo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:367
translate spanish d9a0_b0e7b3fa:

    # Q "You know Stalker [persistent.player_name] by now, there is no need for formalities."
    Q "Ya conoces al Acechador [persistent.player_name], no hay necesidad de formalidades."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:368
translate spanish d9a0_7992cfce:

    # Q "Please take care of [Mi] while I discuss matters."
    Q "Por favor, ocúpate de [Mi] mientras yo discuto los asuntos."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:369
translate spanish d9a0_8b786057:

    # Q "You can leave."
    Q "Puedes marcharte."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:371
translate spanish d9a0_753e8031:

    # Q "Stalker [persistent.player_name]'s lack of respect will be dealt with another time. We have a situation to solve first."
    Q "La falta de respeto del Acechador  [persistent.player_name] será tratada en otro momento. Primero tenemos que resolver una situación."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:372
translate spanish d9a0_6e3e14ee:

    # Q "Go ahead and take care of [Mi] while I discuss the matter with him."
    Q "Ve a ocuparte de [Mi] mientras yo discuto el asunto con él."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:373
translate spanish d9a0_8b786057_1:

    # Q "You can leave."
    Q "Puedes marcharte."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:376
translate spanish d9a0_fba45575:

    # Sh "As you wish, my Queen."
    Sh "Como quieras, mi Reina."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:379
translate spanish d9a0_a524de27:

    # "Sharifa leaves..."
    "Sharifa se va..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:383
translate spanish d9a0_9e3e9d61:

    # Q "Don't mind Sharifa, she doesn't trust anyone. Especially not when they're disrupting royal schedules."
    Q "No hagas caso a Sharifa, no se fía de nadie. Y menos cuando alteran los horarios reales."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:385
translate spanish d9a0_e5196f5c:

    # Q "I would be lying if I said Sharifa had no reason to question your presence, and she's not used to your attitude..."
    Q "Mentiría si dijera que Sharifa no tiene motivos para cuestionar tu presencia, y que no está acostumbrada a tu actitud..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:388
translate spanish d9a0_c75d7799:

    # Q "Anyway, I guess you heard what just happened..."
    Q "De todos modos, supongo que has oído lo que acaba de ocurrir..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:391
translate spanish d9a0_f13d28d1:

    # Q "And as you might guess, that's why you're here again. I have a new task for you."
    Q "Y como podrás adivinar, por eso estás aquí de nuevo. Tengo una nueva tarea para ti."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:394
translate spanish d9a0_60edc387:

    # Q "But first, tell me... is [S] alright? She's scouting the Zone now, isn't she?"
    Q "Pero antes, dime... ¿está bien [S]? Ahora está explorando la Zona, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:398
translate spanish d9a0_52cc7be9:

    # Z "She has returned, actually. She came home at night."
    Z "De hecho, ha vuelto. Volvió a casa por la noche."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:401
translate spanish d9a0_c6ca2bfe:

    # Q "Has she? I... am very glad."
    Q "¿Lo ha hecho? Yo... me alegro mucho."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:402
translate spanish d9a0_2d14ab47:

    # Q "I will have you both over to discuss what happened, but I need you to take care of another matter first."
    Q "Os invitaré a los dos para hablar de lo ocurrido, pero antes necesito que te ocupes de otro asunto."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:404
translate spanish d9a0_5fc9f582:

    # Z "She is out there, yes. She's on her own."
    Z "Está ahí fuera, sí. Está sola."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:407
translate spanish d9a0_b544002e:

    # Q "I see, then we will have to hope for the best."
    Q "Ya veo, entonces tendremos que esperar lo mejor."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:411
translate spanish d9a0_e1a0a989:

    # Q "Look, the reason why I called you, and not one of my soldiers, is that you can act as a neutral party, and they cannot."
    Q "Mira, la razón por la que te he llamado a ti, y no a uno de mis soldados, es porque tú puedes actuar como una parte neutral y ellos no."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:412
translate spanish d9a0_fa7ea61f:

    # Q "One of our caravans, which my soldiers were supposed to protect, was attacked by raiders."
    Q "Una de nuestras caravanas, que se suponía que mis soldados debían proteger, fue atacada por saqueadores."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:415
translate spanish d9a0_a0f1d14a:

    # Q "Before I send my troops over there, I need to know whether or not the raiders attacked more than a handful of my troops."
    Q "Antes de enviar mis tropas allí, necesito saber si los asaltantes atacaron o no a más de un puñado de mis tropas."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:418
translate spanish d9a0_4bf28be4:

    # Q "That's where you come in."
    Q "Ahí es donde entras tú."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:422
translate spanish d9a0_3d94f88d:

    # Q "Look, I know we've had our differences, but since you did valuable-"
    Q "Escucha, sé que hemos tenido nuestras diferencias, pero ya que hiciste valioso..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:423
translate spanish d9a0_17808bec:

    # Z "{i}*sighs*"
    Z "{i}*suspiros*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:426
translate spanish d9a0_125a93d2_1:

    # Q "...?"
    Q "¿...?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:427
translate spanish d9a0_6fc31ead:

    # Z "Please, cut the crap."
    Z "Por favor, déjate de tonterías."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:428
translate spanish d9a0_0386a790:

    # Z "You can act tough in front of them, not me."
    Z "Puedes hacerte la dura delante de ellos, no de mí."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:431
translate spanish d9a0_0a673624:

    # Z "Tell me straight, why am I here and why do you need me?"
    Z "Dime directamente, ¿por qué estoy aquí y por qué me necesitas?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:434
translate spanish d9a0_2ad04f97:

    # Q "Fine..."
    Q "Bien..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:435
translate spanish d9a0_384e96c0:

    # Q "Raiders have been spotted around one of the settlements in the north-east we have a trade agreement with."
    Q "Se han avistado asaltantes alrededor de uno de los asentamientos del noreste con los que tenemos un acuerdo comercial."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:438
translate spanish d9a0_d7d9b3d4:

    # Q "It is a recent settlement, and one caravan that was supposed to pass through it was also raided recently, despite the protection of my patrol."
    Q "Es un asentamiento reciente, y una caravana que debía pasar por él también fue asaltada recientemente, a pesar de la protección de mi patrulla."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:439
translate spanish d9a0_20ec9166:

    # Q "I need you to head over there as a neutral party, and see whether or not the raiders also attacked the settlement itself. If so, try to either solve the situation or report back."
    Q "Necesito que te dirijas allí como parte neutral, y veas si los asaltantes también atacaron el asentamiento en sí. Si es así, trata de resolver la situación o infórmate."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:452
translate spanish d9a76_0a373f9a:

    # Z "When do you want me to head there?"
    Z "¿Cuándo quieres que me dirija allí?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:455
translate spanish d9a76_082540de:

    # Q "Either the settlement has already been overrun, or the raiders have gone back to Adira with what they looted from the caravan, so you decide when you want to take it on."
    Q "O el asentamiento ya ha sido invadido, o los asaltantes han vuelto a Adira con lo que han saqueado de la caravana, así que tú decides cuándo quieres enfrentarte a él."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:456
translate spanish d9a76_6146c8bc:

    # Q "I wouldn't wait too long however, they may be planning another raid soon."
    Q "Sin embargo, no esperaría demasiado, puede que estén planeando otra incursión pronto."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:461
translate spanish d9a76_d8d8de96:

    # Z "I overheard you talking about a girl with purple hair."
    Z "Te he oído hablar de una chica con el pelo morado."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:462
translate spanish d9a76_557a91ee:

    # Z "What was that about?"
    Z "¿De qué se trata?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:465
translate spanish d9a76_af5a0e95:

    # Q "If you were listening, you know as much as me about it."
    Q "Si estabas escuchando, sabes tanto como yo al respecto."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:466
translate spanish d9a76_1bc9c28d:

    # Q "Apparently [Mi]'s platoon was overwhelmed by a small group of raiders led by a girl with purple hair. He said she fought like a psycho."
    Q "Al parecer, el pelotón de [Mi] fue arrollado por un pequeño grupo de asaltantes dirigido por una chica de pelo morado. Dijo que luchó como una psicópata."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:469
translate spanish d9a76_7d832311:

    # Q "After escaping the assault, he barely made it back here."
    Q "Después de escapar del asalto, a duras penas consiguió volver aquí."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:470
translate spanish d9a76_d9307b3f:

    # Q "It's an embarrassment really."
    Q "En realidad es una vergüenza."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:473
translate spanish d9a76_16c6a808:

    # Zt "Interesting. If that's Kyra and her gang, my mission might just be simpler than expected."
    Zt "Es interesante. Si se trata de Kyra y su banda, mi misión podría ser más sencilla de lo esperado."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:478
translate spanish d9a76_426adc3a:

    # Z "Where is the settlement located?"
    Z "¿Dónde se encuentra el asentamiento?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:481
translate spanish d9a76_8b1d9f1b:

    # Q "Do you know the ancient cut-off highway area in the north east?"
    Q "¿Conoces la antigua zona de carreteras cortadas en el noreste?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:484
translate spanish d9a76_235aff8c:

    # Z "A settlement, there? That is on Adira's doorstep."
    Z "¿Un asentamiento, allí? Está a las puertas de Adira."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:487
translate spanish d9a76_620cf51d:

    # Q "Well, it's not that I have to live there, I guess that where there's water to be found, people will find a way to live."
    Q "Bueno, no es que tenga que vivir allí, supongo que donde hay agua, la gente encontrará la manera de vivir."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:492
translate spanish d9a76_b1981f96:

    # Z "What exactly do you want me to accomplish there?"
    Z "¿Qué es exactamente lo que quieres que consiga allí?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:493
translate spanish d9a76_4a2ed520:

    # Z "And why does that settlement matter so much to you?"
    Z "¿Y por qué te importa tanto ese asentamiento?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:496
translate spanish d9a76_03dd8828:

    # Q "I didn't want to get into the politics of this, [persistent.player_name], but if you must know... if we are to expand our influence and protect our resources, we have to secure trade routes."
    Q "No quería entrar en la política de esto, [persistent.player_name], pero si debes saberlo... Si queremos ampliar nuestra influencia y proteger nuestros recursos, tenemos que asegurar las rutas comerciales."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:497
translate spanish d9a76_c6b72b16:

    # Q "My military advisors have reported a steady rise in aggression and numbers in the Raiders from the barren regions for some time now."
    Q "Mis asesores militares han informado de un aumento constante de la agresividad y del número de Asaltantes de las regiones áridas desde hace tiempo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:498
translate spanish d9a76_c82a5f3c:

    # Q "A settlement or two along the routes, loyal to us, would be the most effective way to both protect the caravans and stop the Raiders pushing at our borders. Or so we thought."
    Q "Un asentamiento o dos a lo largo de las rutas, leales a nosotros, sería la forma más eficaz tanto de proteger las caravanas como de detener a los Asaltantes que presionan en nuestras fronteras. O eso pensamos."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:501
translate spanish d9a76_0af8f3a0:

    # Q "We are trying to limit our deployment of troops in the area by giving them defensible positions and local support."
    Q "Estamos intentando limitar el despliegue de tropas en la zona, dándoles posiciones defendibles y apoyo local."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:502
translate spanish d9a76_45f0a4c9:

    # Q "It is simply too dangerous for anybody to be caught between Old Cairo and Adira..."
    Q "Es sencillamente demasiado peligroso para cualquiera que se encuentre entre el Viejo Cairo y Adira..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:503
translate spanish d9a76_0a169642:

    # Q "...so we are trying to create a self-sufficient settlement, with a little nudge and the promise of protection when needed."
    Q "... así que estamos intentando crear un asentamiento autosuficiente, con un pequeño empujón y la promesa de protección cuando sea necesario."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:506
translate spanish d9a76_f017f546:

    # Q "This means potentially giving the new settlements a degree of freedom to decide their fate for themselves as long as they are useful to us."
    Q "Esto significa dar potencialmente a los nuevos asentamientos un grado de libertad para decidir su destino por sí mismos mientras nos sean útiles."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:507
translate spanish d9a76_c955d931:

    # Q "So, scouting mission aside, what I really want is for you to make sure the settlement does not become hostile towards us."
    Q "Así que, dejando de lado la misión de exploración, lo que realmente quiero es que te asegures de que el asentamiento no se vuelva hostil hacia nosotros."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:512
translate spanish d9a76_740a260c:

    # Z "You're not sending your soldiers because they could be killed, but raiders are unpredictable. What if things go south and I don't report back?"
    Z "No envías a tus soldados porque podrían morir, pero los asaltantes son impredecibles. ¿Qué pasa si las cosas van mal y no regreso a informar?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:515
translate spanish d9a76_f36df0bb:

    # Q "The settlement is not that far from here, your vehicle should get you there within a few hours."
    Q "El asentamiento no está muy lejos de aquí, tu vehículo debería llevarte allí en unas horas."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:516
translate spanish d9a76_b7643aa3:

    # Q "When you decide to head there, I will give you four days to report back."
    Q "Cuando decidas dirigirte allí, te daré cuatro días para que me informes."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:519
translate spanish d9a76_b2a3b6fa:

    # Q "In case you are killed or captured or otherwise don't report back, I will take it as a a sign that the settlement has been overrun or turned and send out the troops to burn it to the ground."
    Q "En caso de que te maten o te capturen o no te informes, lo tomaré como una señal de que el asentamiento ha sido invadido o convertido y enviaré a las tropas para que lo quemen hasta los cimientos."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:520
translate spanish d9a76_56638086:

    # Q "And yes, if you need to play that card, feel free to tell the raiders, or even the settlers, that the sword of Zeta is pointed in their direction."
    Q "Y sí, si necesitas jugar esa carta, no dudes en decir a los asaltantes, o incluso a los colonos, que la espada de Zeta apunta en su dirección."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:538
translate spanish d9a84a_4e604b79:

    # Q "So, will you take the job?"
    Q "¿Aceptas el trabajo?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:543
translate spanish d9a84a_2575b9ff:

    # Z "We have an agreement. You can count on me."
    Z "Tenemos un acuerdo. Puedes contar conmigo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:549
translate spanish d9a84a_0cf4c628:

    # Q "Thank you, [persistent.player_name]."
    Q "Gracias, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:550
translate spanish d9a84a_00d0b033:

    # Q "There seems to be no end to the many problems that can endanger our people. I appreciate that acquiring your help is no such problem."
    Q "Parece que no hay fin a los muchos problemas que pueden poner en peligro a nuestro pueblo. Me parece que conseguir tu ayuda no es un problema."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:556
translate spanish d9a84a_48e17f5c:

    # Z "If it helps Zeta, I'm willing to take the risk."
    Z "Si eso ayuda a Zeta, estoy dispuesto a correr el riesgo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:562
translate spanish d9a84a_096e17cf:

    # Q "I may appear arrogant at times, [persistent.player_name]. But I promise you that almost all I do is for the good of the people of Zeta."
    Q "Puede que a veces parezca arrogante, [persistent.player_name]. Pero te prometo que casi todo lo que hago es por el bien de la gente de Zeta."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:563
translate spanish d9a84a_0a9a84fc:

    # Q "Thank you for your service."
    Q "Gracias por tu servicio."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:569
translate spanish d9a84a_e0f7d293:

    # Z "Fair enough, as long as the reward is right."
    Z "Me parece justo, siempre que la recompensa sea adecuada."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:575
translate spanish d9a84a_86ef12b4:

    # Q "Of course you will be rewarded, like always."
    Q "Por supuesto que serás recompensado, como siempre."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:576
translate spanish d9a84a_bf219a1d:

    # Q "I appreciate the risks you take, no matter your personal motivation to do so. So thank you, [persistent.player_name]."
    Q "Aprecio los riesgos que asumes, independientemente de tu motivación personal para hacerlo. Así que gracias, [persistent.player_name]."

