translate spanish d9a84b_10031513:

    # "You hear Sharifa's voice approaching..."
    "Oyes la voz de Sharifa acercándose..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:881
translate spanish d9a84b_2a1fc93c:

    # Q "I am still in the meeting, Sharifa. One moment."
    Q "Todavía estoy en la reunión, Sharifa. Un momento."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:884
translate spanish d9a84b_b382c8d1:

    # Z "I will let your guard know once the matter is taken care of."
    Z "Informaré a tu guardia una vez que se haya resuelto el asunto."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:885
translate spanish d9a84b_f0604254:

    # Z "Expect to hear back from me soon."
    Z "Espera tener noticias mías pronto."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:891
translate spanish d9a84b_5df7e9c1:

    # Q "I will wait for your signal then, as I said."
    Q "Esperaré entonces tu señal, como he dicho."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:894
translate spanish d9a84b_9efce0f0_3:

    # Q "Be careful out there, [persistent.player_name]..."
    Q "Ten cuidado ahí fuera, [persistent.player_name]..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:897
translate spanish d9a84b_fa2bb28c:

    # Z "Don't worry about it."
    Z "No te preocupes."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:900
translate spanish d9a84b_999a3917:

    # Sh "I'm sorry my Queen, I was just informed about one of our platoons in the west. Apparently there is an issue."
    Sh "Lo siento, mi Reina, me acaban de informar sobre uno de nuestros pelotones en el oeste. Al parecer, hay un problema."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:901
translate spanish d9a84b_b955b62f_3:

    # Q "Hand me the report..."
    Q "Pásame el informe..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:902
translate spanish d9a84b_5eeb2345_3:

    # "You leave..."
    "Te vas..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:907
translate spanish d9b_219a7360:

    # Z "[A], you asked for us to spend some time together. I am free now. Do you want to go for a walk together?"
    Z "[A], me pediste que pasáramos un tiempo juntos. Ahora estoy libre. ¿Quieres que demos un paseo juntos?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:910
translate spanish d9b_3826081a:

    # A "Yes, I'd love to. Should I wear the collar?"
    A "Sí, me encantaría. ¿Debo llevar el collarín?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:913
translate spanish d9b_673d483b:

    # Z "You are with me. You don't need it this time."
    Z "Estás conmigo. Esta vez no lo necesitas."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:916
translate spanish d9b_e4850f57:

    # A "Okay! I will get ready!"
    A "De acuerdo. ¡Me prepararé!"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:921
translate spanish d9b_74b86373:

    # "After a while, you head out together. She leads you to a place in the city that is all too familiar to you..."
    "Después de un rato, salís juntos. Ella te lleva a un lugar de la ciudad que te resulta demasiado familiar..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:925
translate spanish d9b_0271a599:

    # Z "Why did you want to come here?"
    Z "¿Por qué querías venir aquí?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:926
translate spanish d9b_6947bcac:

    # A "You and [S] have mentioned this place often, in the past. Like you've come here a lot."
    A "Tú y [S] habéis mencionado este lugar a menudo, en el pasado. Como si hubierais venido aquí muchas veces."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:929
translate spanish d9b_6d156814:

    # Z "We have, yes. It's a historical place."
    Z "Lo hemos hecho, sí. Es un lugar histórico."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:930
translate spanish d9b_9e96d36e:

    # A "And why's that?"
    A "¿Y por qué?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:933
translate spanish d9b_50966892:

    # Z "It's a traditional thing. Whether you're a soldier, Stalker or royal guard, everyone comes here at least once."
    Z "Es algo tradicional. Ya seas soldado, Acechador o guardia real, todo el mundo viene aquí al menos una vez."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:936
translate spanish d9b_38a08c19:

    # Z "They say these are the oldest buildings, where the original founders of Zeta came together first and started to rebuild."
    Z "Dicen que estos son los edificios más antiguos, donde los fundadores originales de Zeta se reunieron primero y empezaron a reconstruir."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:939
translate spanish d9b_4d1eeda5:

    # Z "That's what makes the place worth seeing."
    Z "Eso es lo que hace que merezca la pena ver el lugar."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:940
translate spanish d9b_c1a13b1b:

    # Z "The obelisk represents the first cornerstone, placed over 400 years ago at what was, then, the center of the city."
    Z "El obelisco representa la primera piedra angular, colocada hace más de 400 años en lo que entonces era el centro de la ciudad."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:949
translate spanish d9b_ad05516f:

    # A "Well..."
    A "Bueno..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:950
translate spanish d9b_089a5531:

    # A "They made sure that you can't miss it."
    A "Se aseguraron de que no te lo puedas perder."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:953
translate spanish d9b_7eef7e23:

    # A "I was never really interested in this place, so I've only seen it a couple times."
    A "Nunca me interesó mucho este lugar, así que sólo lo he visto un par de veces."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:954
translate spanish d9b_5e89dace:

    # A "But now that I'm here..."
    A "Pero ahora que estoy aquí..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:957
translate spanish d9b_d8654138:

    # A "..."
    A "..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:960
translate spanish d9b_1adae3fd:

    # A "...I'm still not very interested, to be honest."
    A "... Para ser sincera, sigo sin estar muy interesada."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:961
translate spanish d9b_36522e4b:

    # A "But it was worth coming here with you."
    A "Pero ha merecido la pena venir aquí contigo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:964
translate spanish d9b_07847094:

    # Z "Okay, so what do you want to do now?"
    Z "Vale, ¿qué quieres hacer ahora?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:967
translate spanish d9b_1d357113:

    # A "Do you see those huge windows over there?"
    A "¿Ves esas enormes ventanas de ahí?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:968
translate spanish d9b_900f0148:

    # Z "Hm..."
    Z "Hm..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:971
translate spanish d9b_abdb3b5d:

    # A "I wonder if you can sit in them?"
    A "Me pregunto si puedes sentarte en ellos."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:974
translate spanish d9b_413437d3:

    # Z "Is that a challenge?"
    Z "¿Es un reto?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:977
translate spanish d9b_b6d6a536:

    # "You and [A] head to one of the monuments. She is surprised how quickly you manage to climb up the stone wall."
    "Tú y [A] os dirigís a uno de los monumentos. Ella se sorprende de la rapidez con la que consigues trepar por el muro de piedra."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:980
translate spanish d9b_e963d659:

    # Z "You didn't expect that, did you?"
    Z "No te lo esperabas, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:981
translate spanish d9b_fcb16f7f:

    # A "You're funny. It's not like you're twice as tall as me."
    A "Eres gracioso. No es que seas el doble de alto que yo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:984
translate spanish d9b_d9aa518f:

    # Z "Why don't you join me up here, too?"
    Z "¿Por qué no te unes a mí aquí también?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:985
translate spanish d9b_07b1ccca:

    # Z "I can help you up, if you want."
    Z "Puedo ayudarte a levantarte, si quieres."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:988
translate spanish d9b_976e132f:

    # Z "That is... if you're brave enough."
    Z "Eso es... si eres lo suficientemente valiente."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:991
translate spanish d9b_3ff73fae:

    # A "I'm not like you or [S], I'm not sure if-"
    A "No soy como tú o [S], no estoy segura de si..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:994
translate spanish d9b_d0e1654b:

    # Z "It's not about that. All you need is one good jump and to grab my hand."
    Z "No se trata de eso. Todo lo que necesitas es un buen salto y agarrar mi mano."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:995
translate spanish d9b_fe907882:

    # Z "Come on, I know you can do it."
    Z "Vamos, sé que puedes hacerlo"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:998
translate spanish d9b_efcb6f72:

    # A "Fine... but you better catch me."
    A "Bien... pero será mejor que me cojas."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1001
translate spanish d9b_b2eca365:

    # "She steadies for a moment... gets ready to jump...and..."
    "Se estabiliza un momento... se prepara para saltar... y..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1004
translate spanish d9b_82dc148c:

    # Z "Got you!"
    Z "¡Te tengo!"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1005
translate spanish d9b_e582be5d:

    # A "Are you sure you won't let me fall?"
    A "¿Estás seguro de que no me dejarás caer?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1008
translate spanish d9b_73bdf69c:

    # Z "You are really not that heavy."
    Z "En realidad no eres tan pesada."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1009
translate spanish d9b_c5f39224:

    # Z "Now, I'm going to pull you up."
    Z "Ahora, voy a levantarte."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1012
translate spanish d9b_69a4c93f:

    # A "Don't..."
    A "No..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1013
translate spanish d9b_16c29196:

    # Z "Up you come..."
    Z "Arriba..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1016
translate spanish d9b_ae6e657f:

    # A "Don't drop me, please...!"
    A "No me dejes caer, por favor..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1020
translate spanish d9b_a58053c8:

    # "You successfully pull her up. After taking a moment to recompose yourselves, you both settle down on the windowsill..."
    "La subes con éxito. Después de tomaros un momento para recomponeros, os acomodáis los dos en el umbral de la ventana..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1024
translate spanish d9b_b8848b59:

    # A "I didn't think it would be that easy.."
    A "No pensé que fuera tan fácil.."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1029
translate spanish d9b_08143766:

    # Z "That was a good jump, I didn't know you had it in you."
    Z "Ha sido un buen salto, no sabía que lo tenías en tu interior."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1032
translate spanish d9b_2c0f20f2:

    # A "Maybe I've been secretly practicing with [S] all along."
    A "Tal vez haya estado practicando en secreto con [S] todo el tiempo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1035
translate spanish d9b_04adf841:

    # Z "Maybe you were indeed. Who knows."
    Z "Tal vez sí lo hayas hecho. Quién sabe."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1038
translate spanish d9b_59151231:

    # A "Maybe, yeah... maybe not..."
    A "Tal vez, sí... Tal vez no..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1042
translate spanish d9b_86297904:

    # Z "You shouldn't doubt yourself so much."
    Z "No deberías dudar tanto de ti misma."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1045
translate spanish d9b_eec36fe7:

    # A "I know I do that. Sorry if I was a bit too whiny."
    A "Sé que lo hago. Perdona si he sido demasiado quejica."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1048
translate spanish d9b_e07646f7:

    # Z "You're not whiny. You're just not used to taking initiatives like this. Forget about it."
    Z "No eres una quejica. Simplemente no estás acostumbrada a tomar iniciativas como ésta. Olvídate de ello."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1051
translate spanish d9b_70ddc240:

    # A "I never really bothered with it I guess."
    A "Supongo que nunca me he preocupado por ello."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1057
translate spanish d9b34_7ff75b6d:

    # Z "So, how do you like it up here?"
    Z "¿Qué te parece esto?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1058
translate spanish d9b34_12776826:

    # A "It's nice. It's quiet."
    A "Se está bien. Es tranquilo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1059
translate spanish d9b34_595436a7:

    # Z "It is."
    Z "Lo es."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1062
translate spanish d9b34_b86c589f:

    # "She looks reflective..."
    "Parece reflexiva..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1063
translate spanish d9b34_d8654138:

    # A "..."
    A "..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1064
translate spanish d9b34_bae9b482:

    # Z "What are you thinking about?"
    Z "¿En qué estás pensando?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1067
translate spanish d9b34_71cf9e08:

    # A "I don't know... I guess about why I wanted to come here?"
    A "No sé... Supongo que sobre el motivo por el que quería venir aquí."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1070
translate spanish d9b34_0a8959e5:

    # Z "Which is?"
    Z "¿Cuál es?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1073
translate spanish d9b34_3490b3e0:

    # A "To see what you both spend so much time on, you and [S]."
    A "Para ver en qué pasan tanto tiempo tú y [S]."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1074
translate spanish d9b34_238096ea:

    # A "I have been thinking about it, you know?"
    A "He estado pensando en ello, ¿sabes?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1077
translate spanish d9b34_cd4fa58e:

    # A "I sometimes envy what you both have, what you share..."
    A "A veces envidio lo que tenéis los dos, lo que compartís..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1080
translate spanish d9b34_04fc92a5:

    # Z "What do you mean by both have?"
    Z "¿Qué quieres decir con que ambos tenemos?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1083
translate spanish d9b34_0a6d31f2:

    # A "Well.. you know... you have this place here where you can find people like yourselves..."
    A "Bueno... ya sabes... tienes este lugar aquí donde puedes encontrar gente como vosotros..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1086
translate spanish d9b34_d33e3ae1:

    # A "...you can talk about it, have things in common..."
    A "... podéis hablar de ello, tener cosas en común..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1087
translate spanish d9b34_024b6a58:

    # A "It would be nice to also be part of something more, sometimes..."
    A "Sería bonito también formar parte de algo más, a veces..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1090
translate spanish d9b34_d8654138_1:

    # A "..."
    A "..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1093
translate spanish d9b34_ead98542:

    # A "Now that I am here, and see the places you go to with [S]..."
    A "Ahora que estoy aquí, y veo los lugares a los que vas con [S]..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1096
translate spanish d9b34_644942c6:

    # A "I don't know if I even want anything like that and what it could be."
    A "No sé si quiero algo así y qué podría ser."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1097
translate spanish d9b34_7605c6f6:

    # A "...but it would be nice to know, I guess."
    A "... pero sería bueno saberlo, supongo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1100
translate spanish d9b34_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1101
translate spanish d9b34_89c3c779:

    # Z "I see."
    Z "Ya veo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1111
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_f86b6bce:

    # Z "Is there something you would like to learn, or that you liked learning about particularly?"
    Z "¿Hay algo que te gustaría aprender, o que te haya gustado aprender en particular?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1114
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_51cdd105:

    # A "If only I knew."
    A "Si lo supiera."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1117
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_65c68296:

    # A "I mean... I don't dislike how I spend my time at the moment..."
    A "Es decir... No me disgusta cómo paso mi tiempo en este momento..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1119
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_a5eda8e5:

    # A "I know I'm not exactly productive, but I do like to supervise and direct Emilia sometimes, making sure she does what [persistent.mom] told her to do."
    A "Sé que no soy precisamente productiva, pero a veces me gusta supervisar y dirigir a Emilia, asegurándome de que haga lo que [persistent.mom] le dijo que hiciera."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1122
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_9bdd8048:

    # A "I also like to dress up when we are preparing for our guests, you know..."
    A "También me gusta arreglarme cuando nos preparamos para nuestros invitados, ya sabes..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1124
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_5f5a134d:

    # A "I know it's nothing productive really, but I do like to play dress up, especially when we're preparing for guests, you know."
    A "Sé que no es nada productivo en realidad, pero me gusta jugar a disfrazarme, especialmente cuando nos preparamos para los invitados, ya sabes."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1127
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_541a87b7:

    # A "...and I kind of enjoy their comments... {i}*chuckles*"
    A "... y como disfruto de sus comentarios... {i}*risilla*"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1130
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_f050fbbd:

    # Z "Well, their comments are justified."
    Z "Bueno, sus comentarios están justificados."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1133
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_6c916170:

    # A "Naaw... thank you."
    A "Ohhh... gracias."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1134
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_d8e98393:

    # A "But as I said, not really productive..."
    A "Pero como he dicho, no es realmente productivo..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1139
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_1dab1df9:

    # Z "It depends on what you call productive."
    Z "Depende de lo que llames productivo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1140
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_305258b6:

    # Z "It's all about influence and power nowadays."
    Z "Hoy en día todo es cuestión de influencia y poder."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1141
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_8243eb28:

    # Z "And I say nowadays, but it has always been so. Not only inside this city."
    Z "Y digo que hoy en día, pero siempre ha sido así. No sólo dentro de esta ciudad."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1142
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_d852cb20:

    # Z "People respect status and reputation over most other values. That's why they raised a monument in this place. It's intimidation, nothing more and nothing less."
    Z "La gente respeta el estatus y la reputación por encima de la mayoría de los demás valores. Por eso levantaron un monumento en este lugar. Es una intimidación, nada más y nada menos."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1145
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_f5a24671:

    # A "You're saying I should be more intimidating?"
    A "¿Dices que debería ser más intimidante?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1148
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_5c07bb47:

    # Z "Well... from a certain point of view, you already are."
    Z "Bueno... desde cierto punto de vista, ya lo eres."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1151
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_9da0d7c8:

    # A "What, me?"
    A "¿Qué, yo?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1154
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_b709dfb7:

    # Z "To my guests? Yes. Me having such a pretty [persistent.da] in my house, and on my side..."
    Z "¿A mis invitados? Sí. El hecho de tener a una [persistent.da] tan bonita en mi casa, y a mi lado..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1155
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_bd3448cc:

    # Z "...that leaves an impression. I know why I am inviting them home, when I do."
    Z "... que deja huella. Sé por qué los invito a casa, cuando lo hago."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1157
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_554e2160:

    # Z "If you see it that way, you're the physical representation of the status of our House. {i}*chuckles*"
    Z "Si lo miras así, eres el vivo reflejo del estatus de nuestra Casa. {i}*risilla*"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1159
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_4d7692ed:

    # Z "If you see it that way, it's almost fitting to call you the physical representation of the status of our House. {i}*chuckles*"
    Z "Si lo ves así, es casi apropiado llamarte la representación física del estatus de nuestra Casa. {i}*risilla*"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1162
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_515768a0:

    # A "But what about [S]? She's also very pretty, and smart too."
    A "¿Pero qué pasa con [S]? También es muy guapa, y también inteligente."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1165
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_633cf372:

    # Z "You're no less smart, just in other ways."
    Z "No eres menos inteligente, sólo que en otros aspectos."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1166
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_d2db184a:

    # Z "She maybe knows more about fighting, or the history of things."
    Z "Tal vez ella sepa más sobre la lucha, o la historia de las cosas."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1167
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_d1d62f74:

    # Z "But you and I know that you're a much better people person."
    Z "Pero tú y yo sabemos que eres mucho más sociable."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1168
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_a9224d32:

    # Z "Judging by the conversations you have with our guests..."
    Z "A juzgar por las conversaciones que mantienes con nuestros invitados..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1169
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_37087766:

    # Z "...and by how you interacted with them, even when you were younger..."
    Z "... y por cómo interactuabas con ellos, incluso cuando eras más joven..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1172
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_45373a11:

    # A "{i}*laughs*{/i} Please, I was much worse back then than I am now."
    A "{i}*risas*{/i} Por favor, entonces era mucho peor que ahora."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1175
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_390ce887:

    # A "...but you're not wrong, I guess."
    A "... pero no te equivocas, supongo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1178
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_6ef80a1e:

    # Z "See, I know you better than you do. You have an ease, coupled with the looks to be able to wrap people around your little finger."
    Z "Lo ves, te conozco mejor que tú misma. Tienes un desparpajo y un físico capaces de tener a cualquiera comiendo de tu mano."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1182
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_f6800a99:

    # Z "That's not exactly productive indeed."
    Z "Desde luego, eso no es precisamente productivo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1185
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_792dfb2e:

    # A "I know... but I haven't found much else yet."
    A "Lo sé... pero aún no he encontrado mucho más."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1186
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_f42e025c:

    # A "I am not like [persistent.mom], really."
    A "No soy como [persistent.mom], realmente."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1188
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_4c7ec963:

    # A "And even that girl that visited us is better at cooking than me."
    A "E incluso esa chica que nos visitó es mejor cocinando que yo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1191
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_0a56bdf4:

    # Z "Kateryna?"
    Z "¿Kateryna?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1194
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_11ea656f:

    # A "Yes..."
    A "Sí..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1198
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_070d9563:

    # A "Anyway..."
    A "En fin..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1203
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_30dc8829:

    # Z "Would you like to do more things like your sister?"
    Z "¿Te gustaría hacer más cosas como tu hermana?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1204
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_ffbfad7d:

    # Z "I know you didn't want to back then, but maybe you changed your mind?"
    Z "Sé que entonces no querías, pero tal vez hayas cambiado de opinión."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1207
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_912c8c8b:

    # A "I don't think I'm made for that path, no..."
    A "No creo que esté hecha para ese camino, no..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1210
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_9e969075:

    # A "I really like watching you two doing the things you do, but it's not for me."
    A "Me gusta mucho veros hacer las cosas que hacéis, pero no es para mí."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1213
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_cba6e483:

    # Z "So you're sure about that, at least."
    Z "Así que, al menos, estás segura de ello."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1214
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_674cb581:

    # Z "I know what you mean though. You are looking to find your identity, in a way."
    Z "Sin embargo, sé lo que quieres decir. En cierto modo, buscas encontrar tu identidad."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1217
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_232c1e30:

    # A "Yes, maybe that."
    A "Sí, tal vez."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1223
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_5e9b11c9:

    # Z "But consider this: I didn't choose this path so I could hang out with other people like me."
    Z "Pero considera esto: No elegí este camino para poder juntarme con otras personas como yo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1224
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_8793ea64:

    # Z "Stalkers are mostly alone on their trips anyway. And even that choice was a gamble. Some people never find their true profession even though they try multiple things."
    Z "De todos modos, los Acechadores están casi siempre solos en sus viajes. E incluso esa elección era una apuesta. Algunas personas nunca encuentran su verdadera profesión aunque prueben muchas cosas."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1225
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_be5efe13:

    # Z "Don't let it discourage you. Just keep doing and experimenting with what you like."
    Z "No dejes que te desanime. Sigue haciendo y experimentando con lo que te gusta."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1228
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_dec1e77c:

    # A "I will try. Thanks."
    A "Lo intentaré. Gracias."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1233
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_ee0279db:

    # Z "You don't need all of that."
    Z "No necesitas todo eso."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1234
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_1f156bc7:

    # Z "It's not like I am happier because there are others who do the same things as me."
    Z "No es que sea más feliz porque hay otros que hacen lo mismo que yo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1235
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_20e370b8:

    # Z "I have my friends, my home, and my family."
    Z "Tengo mis amigos, mi casa y mi familia."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1236
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_0bcac655:

    # Z "Those are the thing that matter. And you have all of them already."
    Z "Eso es lo que importa. Y ya las tienes todas."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1239
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_19fd6494:

    # A "I didn't think of it that way, I guess."
    A "No me lo planteé así, supongo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1248
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_e0ea7608:

    # Z "So how about this..."
    Z "Entonces, qué te parece esto..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1249
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_faad7d99:

    # Z "Let's try out some new things in the future, maybe find something that is our thing only."
    Z "Probemos cosas nuevas en el futuro, quizá encontremos algo que sea sólo nuestro."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1250
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_7a5166c1:

    # Z "What do you say?"
    Z "¿Qué dices?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1253
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_3500f636:

    # A "What do you mean by trying out?"
    A "¿Qué quieres decir con probar?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1256
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_b05bb276:

    # Z "Well..."
    Z "Bueno..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1258
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_31ecbf30:

    # Z "You said you liked to prepare for events and to dress up."
    Z "Dijiste que te gustaba prepararte para los eventos y arreglarte."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1259
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_37f8b3a3:

    # Z "Maybe we can do more of that; find a way to take that up a notch."
    Z "Tal vez podamos hacer más de eso; encontrar una forma de subir de nivel."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1261
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_336c904f:

    # Z "You said you don't want to do the things your sister does."
    Z "Dijiste que no querías hacer las cosas que hace tu hermana."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1262
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_16ca92ba:

    # Z "I think I have a good idea what you like and what not."
    Z "Creo que tengo una buena idea de lo que te gusta y lo que no."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1264
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_31ecbf30_1:

    # Z "You said you liked to prepare for events and to dress up."
    Z "Dijiste que te gustaba prepararte para los eventos y arreglarte."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1265
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_912bacfe:

    # Z "You also said you don't want to do the things your sister does."
    Z "También has dicho que no quieres hacer las cosas que hace tu hermana."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1266
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_e2f7535d:

    # Z "Maybe we can explore what lies in that direction, expand on it."
    Z "Quizá podamos explorar lo que hay en esa dirección, ampliarlo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1268
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_648600c1:

    # Z "No need to decide on anything specific right now."
    Z "No es necesario decidir nada concreto ahora mismo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1269
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_9bc7659d:

    # Z "But I'll think of something you might enjoy."
    Z "Pero pensaré en algo que te pueda gustar."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1272
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_a4f193e0:

    # A "Okay, now I'm curious. But it sounds cool."
    A "Vale, ahora tengo curiosidad. Pero suena bien."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1277
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_e1db0cfc:

    # Z "Hey, come here."
    Z "Eh, ven aquí."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1280
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_9d79e5db:

    # A "Okay."
    A "De acuerdo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1283
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_717253e8:

    # Z "I know it's not easy sometimes."
    Z "Sé que a veces no es fácil."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1284
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_5def269b:

    # Z "Especially when everyone else looks like they have it all sorted out."
    Z "Sobre todo cuando todos los demás parecen tenerlo todo resuelto."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1287
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_f3b03b19:

    # Z "But I can promise you, everyone has their doubts."
    Z "Pero puedo prometerte que todo el mundo tiene sus dudas."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1288
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_1b161438:

    # Z "Even those who already know what their ambition in life is."
    Z "Incluso los que ya saben cuál es su ambición en la vida."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1291
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_4adaf1fc:

    # Z "You know what you want, deep down. And you don't need someone else to tell you what it is."
    Z "En el fondo sabes lo que quieres. Y no necesitas que otra persona te diga lo que es."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1292
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_89f128eb:

    # Z "I love you and [S] equally, no matter what your role is or may become, both in the House or outside."
    Z "Os quiero a ti y a [S] por igual, independientemente del papel que desempeñéis o podáis desempeñar, tanto en la Casa como fuera de ella."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1293
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_8ac31058:

    # Z "You are not better or worse than your sister. You both are unique, and I would not want you any other way than that."
    Z "No eres mejor ni peor que tu hermana. Ambas sois únicas, y no os querría de otra manera."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1296
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_d8654138:

    # A "..."
    A "..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1299
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_dc61a007:

    # A "Thank you, [persistent.dad]."
    A "Gracias, [persistent.dad]."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1302
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_a5d746bf:

    # Z "...!"
    Z "¡...!"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1305
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_d021afea:

    # Z "Spending some time together was a good idea. In a way, I {i}have{/i} missed you."
    Z "Pasar un tiempo juntos era una buena idea. En cierto modo, te {i}he{/i} echado de menos."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1308
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_a7596610:

    # Z "If you want to do this again, just let me know."
    Z "Si quieres volver a hacerlo, dímelo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1311
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_13ed707f:

    # A "I will, it feels nice to be here with you."
    A "Lo haré, es agradable estar aquí contigo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1317
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_dec4858b:

    # "You spend some time in each other's arms..."
    "Pasáis un rato entre los brazos del otro..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1318
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_7a907f48:

    # "After which, you both decide to climb down the monument and head back home."
    "Tras lo cual, ambos decidís bajar del monumento y volver a casa."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1325
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_28eb365d:

    # Z "So what do you say... I could use a drink."
    Z "Entonces, qué dices... Me vendría bien un trago."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1328
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_902de067:

    # A "Me too, for sure."
    A "A mí también, sin duda."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1331
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_f2ed6936:

    # Z "Then let's get down from here. I'll go first."
    Z "Entonces bajemos de aquí. Yo iré primero."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1335
translate spanish d9b_dialogue_end_8f7158ad:

    # "After jumping down, you catch [A] as she lets herself glide into your arms, and eventually head back home..."
    "Después de saltar, coges a [A] mientras ella se deja deslizar en tus brazos, y finalmente te diriges a tu casa..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1340
translate spanish d9c_1976349d:

    # Z "Time for a groceries run."
    Z "Es hora de hacer la compra."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1343
translate spanish d9c_73f257f7:

    # "You head to the market. As you take notice of the time of day, you hope to still find a few stalls."
    "Te diriges al mercado. Al fijarte en la hora, esperas encontrar todavía algunos puestos."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1350
translate spanish d9c_c9401261:

    # Zt "At least I'm not too late. They are winding down for the day, though."
    Zt "Al menos no he llegado demasiado tarde. Sin embargo, están terminando el día."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1351
translate spanish d9c_02b0cd41:

    # Zt "Let's see whats on the list... spices, meat, coal..."
    Zt "Veamos qué hay en la lista... especias, carne, carbón..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1354
translate spanish d9c_36cf1810:

    # "As you walk in between stalls, you see someone you recognize..."
    "Mientras caminas entre los puestos, ves a alguien que reconoces..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1357
translate spanish d9c_d3296577:

    # Wom "Filth! I hope you are learning your lesson!"
    Wom "¡Mugre! ¡Espero que estés aprendiendo la lección!"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1358
translate spanish d9c_1625da63:

    # Zt "Isn't that..."
    Zt "¿No es esa...?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1361
translate spanish d9c_fcbc5652:

    # "You step closer..."
    "Te acercas más..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1364
translate spanish d9c_7c2f5470:

    # Wom "You can play dead all you want. Tomorrow's another day, and you'll be here again."
    Wom "Puedes hacerte la muerta todo lo que quieras. Mañana será otro día y volverás a estar aquí."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1365
translate spanish d9c_364c25f6:

    # Wom "You should have met the same fate as your partner, if you ask me."
    Wom "Deberías correr la misma suerte que tu compañero, en mi opinión."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1366
translate spanish d9c_fbf366ff:

    # Wom "That would've been true justice."
    Wom "Eso habría sido verdadera justicia."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1369
translate spanish d9c_45e6d9e5:

    # Z "I remember her."
    Z "Me acuerdo de ella."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1372
translate spanish d9c_6b9be373:

    # Z "She's the would be kidnapper who survived."
    Z "Ella es la supuesta secuestradora que sobrevivió."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1375
translate spanish d9c_64e53a5e:

    # Wom "She has done a lot worse than that."
    Wom "Ella ha hecho cosas mucho peores."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1376
translate spanish d9c_3cb0f0c4:

    # Wom "People have found out that she was involved in a lot more crimes."
    Wom "La gente ha descubierto que estaba implicada en muchos más crímenes."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1377
translate spanish d9c_23f21f8e:

    # Wom "She's getting off too easy, if you ask me."
    Wom "En mi opinión, se está librando con demasiada facilidad."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1380
translate spanish d9c_abb89930:

    # Tg "{i}*exhausted breathing*"
    Tg "{i}*respiración agotada*"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1381
translate spanish d9c_49b0c26b:

    # G "It's getting late, Stalker. The servant needs to rest."
    G "Se hace tarde, Acechador. La sirvienta necesita descansar."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1384
translate spanish d9c_c7f7068a:

    # G "I'm about to bring her back into the cell for the night, she's had a long day."
    G "Estoy a punto de devolverla a la celda para que pase la noche, ha tenido un largo día."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1385
translate spanish d9c_df1ce7fe:

    # G "People really don't like her for the things she did, but she should be able to serve out her sentence as commanded by the Queen."
    G "La gente no la quiere por las cosas que hizo, pero debería poder cumplir su condena tal y como lo ordenó la Reina."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1388
translate spanish d9c_3add0e96:

    # Z "I know who she is, the Queen herself showed her to me after she was caught."
    Z "Sé quién es, la propia Reina me la mostró después de que la atraparan."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1389
translate spanish d9c_7276f34c:

    # Z "It was my [persistent.da] that she tried to kidnap, when she was captured."
    Z "Fue mi [persistent.da] la que intentó secuestrar, cuando fue capturada."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1392
translate spanish d9c_9ce68c49:

    # G "Then I change my mind. She will work overtime today."
    G "Entonces cambio de opinión. Hoy trabajará horas extras."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1393
translate spanish d9c_7959aae9:

    # G "You have every right to give this rat what she deserves, Stalker."
    G "Tienes todo el derecho a darle a esta rata lo que se merece, Acechador."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1396
translate spanish d9c_53b7709a:

    # Tg "..."
    Tg "..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1397
translate spanish d9c_a7fbd9fb:

    # Z "You heard me? Time to wake up again."
    Z "¿Me has oído? Es hora de despertarse de nuevo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1400
translate spanish d9c_f2cce9c2:

    # Tg "...?"
    Tg "¿...?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1404
translate spanish d9c_09eb00ea:

    # Z "Are you regretting your choices yet?"
    Z "¿Ya te estás arrepintiendo de tus decisiones?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1407
translate spanish d9c_78f179d2:

    # Tg "And why would I tell you, anyway?"
    Tg "¿Y por qué iba a decírtelo?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1414
translate spanish d9c_81df170a:

    # Z "Do you know who I am?"
    Z "¿Sabes quién soy?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1417
translate spanish d9c_0438cce3:

    # Tg "{i}*chuckles*{/i} Why, should I?"
    Tg "{i}*risilla*{/i} ¿Por qué, debería hacerlo?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1418
translate spanish d9c_a89f285d:

    # Tg "You look like just another guy in need of a power trip."
    Tg "Pareces el típico tío que necesita subirse el ego."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1425
translate spanish d9c_236b25c4:

    # Z "You look disgusting."
    Z "Tienes un aspecto repugnante."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1428
translate spanish d9c_a4a2e763:

    # Tg "Tell me something I don't know, asshole."
    Tg "Dime algo que no sepa, imbécil."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1435
translate spanish d9c_51c731f8:

    # Z "My [persistent.da] should've killed you."
    Z "Mi [persistent.da] debería haberte matado."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1438
translate spanish d9c_28302796:

    # Tg "Your [persistent.da], you say? Interesting..."
    Tg "¿Tu [persistent.da], dices? Interesante..."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1441
translate spanish d9c_559eaa66:

    # Tg "I wonder if that bitch was as ugly as you."
    Tg "Me pregunto si esa perra era tan fea como tú."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1442
translate spanish d9c_50abeb78:

    # Tg "Unfortunately, all I remember was someone bashing my head."
    Tg "Por desgracia, lo único que recuerdo es que alguien me golpeó en la cabeza."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1450
translate spanish d9cx_a719a037:

    # Z "You tried to kidnap my youngest [persistent.da]."
    Z "Has intentado secuestrar a mi [persistent.da] menor."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1454
translate spanish d9cx_e654a0cc:

    # Tg "Oh, that cow was your [persistent.da]?"
    Tg "Oh, ¿esa vaca era tu [persistent.da]?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1455
translate spanish d9cx_add764d2:

    # Tg "Now that you mention it, I regret it even less."
    Tg "Ahora que lo mencionas, lo lamento aún menos."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1456
translate spanish d9cx_af762c5a:

    # Tg "A Stalker's [persistent.da] would've been quite the trophy for my customers."
    Tg "Una [persistent.da] de un Acechador habría sido todo un trofeo para mis clientes."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1459
translate spanish d9cx_bd688e64:

    # Tg "Is there anything else you want, asshole?"
    Tg "¿Hay algo más que quieras, gilipollas?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1467
translate spanish d9cx_c30bf368:

    # Tg "So that's who you are, hm?"
    Tg "¿Así que eso es lo que eres, um?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1468
translate spanish d9cx_62f07a1b:

    # Tg "...a [persistent.dad] come to avenge his [persistent.da], how cute."
    Tg "... un [persistent.dad] que viene a vengar a su [persistent.da], qué bonito."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1471
translate spanish d9cx_05ed1949:

    # Tg "Sadly I couldn't give less of a shit."
    Tg "Lamentablemente, me importa un bledo."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1479
translate spanish d9cx_91767d00:

    # Tg "That is indeed something I didn't know."
    Tg "Eso es algo que no sabía."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1480
translate spanish d9cx_1cd88f96:

    # Tg "Unfortunately for you, I don't give a flying fuck about who your [persistent.da] was."
    Tg "Por desgracia para ti, me importa una soberana mierda quién fuera tu [persistent.da]."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1483
translate spanish d9cx_454684de:

    # Tg "All I cared about was that she would have made me a good sum, though."
    Tg "Lo único que me importaba era que me habría dado una buena suma de oro."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1491
translate spanish d9cx_680657a7:

    # Tg "How cute, one sister saving the other."
    Tg "Qué bonito, una hermana salvando a la otra."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1492
translate spanish d9cx_084aa40d:

    # Tg "Shame our plan didn't work out."
    Tg "Es una pena que nuestro plan no haya funcionado."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1493
translate spanish d9cx_2d07d892:

    # Tg "I would've been paid very nicely."
    Tg "Me habrían pagado muy bien."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1499
translate spanish d9cx_4a3eee82:

    # Z "Tough talk for someone in your position."
    Z "Palabras duras para alguien en tu posición."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1502
translate spanish d9cx_a39c79f1:

    # Tg "Just because I have been sentenced to this form of punishment, it doesn't mean I have to suck up to every asshole that I come across."
    Tg "Que me hayan condenado a este castigo no significa que tenga que lamerle el culo a cada gilipollas con el que me cruce."

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1511
translate spanish d9c_decision_99f92604:

    # Z "Why did you do it?"
    Z "¿Por qué lo hiciste?"

# game/scripts/day9.rpy:1514
translate spanish d9c_decision_a7bae804:

    # Tg "Why do you think?"
